{"questionId":"13421008","questionHtml":"<p>Find&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>Im</mi><mo> </mo><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;in the form&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi><mo> </mo><mi>sin</mi><mo> </mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>q</mi></mrow></mfenced></math>, where&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></math>,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℝ</mi></math>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>-</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><mo>≤</mo><mi>q</mi><mo>≤</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>t</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">i</mi></mrow></msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>+</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><mn>6</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">i</mi></mrow></msup></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><em>(M1)</em></strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>t</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">i</mi></mrow></msup><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>×</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>90931</mn><mo>…</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>350879</mn><m